this is a nginx module developed by cpp(c++ or cplus cplus)

install and useage:

0.the file path should be changed according to your existing situation.

1.cd ~/nginx-1.8.0

2.cp -rv ~/downloads/nginx-module-developed-by-cpp-master.zip ./

3.unzip nginx-module-developed-by-cpp-master.zip

4.cp -rv nginx-module-developed-by-cpp-master/cpphelloworld/ ./

5. ./configure  --add-module=cpphelloworld

6. cp -rv nginx-module-developed-by-cpp-master/Makefile objs/

7. make

8. sudo make install

9. sudo cp -rv nginx-module-developed-by-cpp-master/nginx.conf /usr/local/nginx/conf/

10. sudo /usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx

11. curl 127.0.0.1/test

then get the "hello world",it is ok! 



